  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Save Earth through yoga &amp; meditation in Costa Rica</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">203 children from schools in high-risk communities in Costa Rica invite you to be part of the answer to save Mother Earth. Through yoga and meditation, they are learning and teaching to create conscious, healthy and sustainable lifestyles. To scale the project around the country, declared Champion of the Earth 2019 by UN, yoga and meditation were declared of public interest; the project was declared of educational interest; and, the Ministry of Education signed a Work Plan with Gaia Foundation.</narrative>
  </description>
